column18: 01/15/2013: Gunmen fired into the house of former prime minister Said Musa in Belize City, Belize, Belize. No one was injured in the attack; however, the house was damaged. No group claimed responsibility for the incident.
column97: Nine millimeter bullets were used in the attack.
column108: The front door of a civilian home and a vehicle were damaged in this attack.
